    <section id="research">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Research</h2>
      <p>Dr Durgungoz’s work centres on the following areas:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
        <li>Developmental Language Disorder (DLD)</li>
        <li>Special Educational Needs (SEN)</li>
        <li>Inclusive education and digital tools</li>
        <li>Emotion coaching and parent-led interventions</li>
      </ul>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-medium mt-4">Selected Publications</h3>
<ul class="list-disc list-inside">
  <li>"We are much closer here": exploring the use of WhatsApp as a learning environment in a secondary school mathematics class. A Durgungoz, FC Durgungoz. <i>Learning Environments Research</i>, 1–22. (Cited by 53, 2021)</li>
  <li>Exploring the Use of Touchscreen Devices for Children with Special Educational Needs and Disabilities: Digital vs Traditional. FC Durgungoz, A Durgungoz. <i>European Journal of Special Education Research</i>, 7(1), 92–109. (Cited by 11, 2021)</li>
  <li>Decision Making of Speech and Language Therapists: Science or Intuition? FC Durgungoz, A Emerson. <i>International Journal of Disability, Development and Education</i>, 1–17. (Cited by 8, 2021)</li>
  <li>Engaging with parents in decision-making: The dilemma of the ideal and reality. FC Durgungoz, A Emerson. <i>Speech, Language and Hearing</i>, 1–16. (Cited by 4, 2021)</li>
  <li>Relying on informal sources in speech and language therapy: why and how? FC Durgungoz. <i>European Journal of Special Education Research</i>, 7(3), 37–72. (Cited by 3, 2021)</li>
  <li>An interactive technology-based emotion recognition intervention for children with developmental language disorder: A longitudinal mixed-method study. FC Durgungoz, MC St Clair. <i>European Journal of Special Needs Education</i>, 1–17. (Cited by 2, 2024)</li>
  <li>Enhancing Parental Understanding of Emotions in Children with Developmental Language Disorder: An Online Parent-Led Intervention Program. FC Durgungoz, MC St Clair. <i>Healthcare</i>, 12(16), 1–17. (Cited by 1, 2024)</li>
  <li>Speech and language therapists' decision-making process: exploring factors behind intervention decisions for children with developmental language disorder in Turkey. FC Durgungoz. <i>University of Nottingham</i>. (2019)</li>
  <li>“Interactive lessons are great, but too much is too much”: Hearing out neurodivergent students, Universal Design for Learning and the case for integrating more anonymous feedback. FC Durgungoz, A Durgungoz. <i>Higher Education</i>, 1–20. (2025)</li>
  <li>A Qualitative Exploration of the Design and Use of e-Learning Activities: Insights from Parents of Children with Developmental Language Disorder. FC Durgungoz, MC St Clair. <i>10th International Conference on e-Society, e-Learning and e-Technologies</i>. (2024)</li>
  <li>Mülteci Ebeveynler ve Çocukları için Duygu Koçluğu Müdahale Programı: Bir Eylem Araştırması. FC Durgungoz. <i>Milli Eğitim Dergisi</i>, 53(242), 713–740. (2024)</li>
  <li>A Parent-led Online Emotion Recognition Intervention for Children with DLD: Has the Intervention Had an Impact on Parents’ Beliefs about Children’s Emotions? FC Durgungoz, M St Clair, C Dack, E Jackson. <i>Uluslararası V. Çocuk Gelişimi Kongresi</i>. (2023)</li>
  <li>Exploring the Impact of an Interactive Technology-based Emotion Recognition Intervention for Children with DLD. FC Durgungoz, C Dack, E Jackson, M St Clair. <i>International Developmental Language Disorder Research Conference (IDLDRC)</i>. (2023)</li>
  <li>Çocuk Gelişimi Terimler Sözlüğü. G Akoğlu, N Aral, Ş Ceylan, E Metin, K Tepeli, F Turan, F C Durgungoz, et al. <i>Nobel</i>. (2023)</li>
  <li>The Use of Emotion Coaching Approach as an Intervention Method for Refugee Parents and Children. FC Durgungoz. <i>IXth International Eurasian Educational Research Congress</i>, 1117–1118. (2022)</li>
  <li>İngiltere’de Annesi ile Oyun Gruplarına Katılan Yabancı Uyruklu Çocukların (0–4 Yaş) Okula Uyum, İkinci Dil ve Sosyal-Duygusal Gelişimlerinin İncelenmesi. FC Durgungoz. <i>5. Ulusal Disiplinerarası Erken Çocuklukta Müdahale Kongresi</i>, 83. (2020)</li>
  <li>Tablet Bilgisayar Kullanımının Özel Gereksinimli Çocuklar Üzerindeki Etkisi. FC Durgungoz, A Durgungoz. <i>5. Ulusal Disiplinerarası Erken Çocuklukta Müdahale Kongresi</i>, 45. (2020)</li>
</ul>
